{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/sampson/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"Sampson Store","caption":"","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#e82828","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/bc51f/sampson-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/41200/sampson-logo.png 165w,\n/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/f979a/sampson-logo.png 330w,\n/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/bc51f/sampson-logo.png 660w","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/322ad/sampson-logo.webp 165w,\n/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/de3b3/sampson-logo.webp 330w,\n/static/10570e0059f7d08d4307b342f305d35b/2b2b5/sampson-logo.webp 660w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400}}}},"body":"<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\">\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sampsonstore.com/neovision/condom/home/index.is?locale=enus\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Check out their shop (Warning: NSFW)</u></a></p>\n<p>Well....Every industry needs programmers! This has been one of the most enjoable part time experience I have ever had back in 2021. Not only did I gained more insights on the sexual well-being retail market, but I also got the chance to refine my Python backend skills, as well as my MySQL knowledge.</p>\n<h2>Shopify Connector</h2>\n<p>SampsonStore is also an exculsive distributor of various condom brands, including Sagami and MyOne Condoms. They have even set up their Shopify page exclusively for MyOne Condoms. During my 4-month part time, I implemented a connecotr in Python to synchronize the internal stock data with that displayed on Shopify Page.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.myonecondoms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Check out their Shopify page! (Warning: NSFW)</u></a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.18181818181818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/c9b55/shopify-api.webp 165w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/f2908/shopify-api.webp 330w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/cc661/shopify-api.webp 660w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/97d4f/shopify-api.webp 827w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/27f9f/shopify-api.jpg 165w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/80fc7/shopify-api.jpg 330w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/ee745/shopify-api.jpg 660w,\n/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/7ab72/shopify-api.jpg 827w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b9ad9a59bfa73b00ce1e4cd91eff365f/ee745/shopify-api.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Sampson Store\"\n            title=\"Sampson Store\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Shopee SG Connector</h2>\n<p>SampsonStore is also establishing its sales channel across multiple E-Commerce platforms, one of them being Shopee, which is a popular E-Commerce platform in Asia. I have also implemented a connecotr in Python to synchronize the internal stock data with that displayed on Shopee.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.63636363636363%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/c9b55/shopee-open-api.webp 165w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/f2908/shopee-open-api.webp 330w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/cc661/shopee-open-api.webp 660w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/a66df/shopee-open-api.webp 990w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/5375b/shopee-open-api.webp 1135w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/04c57/shopee-open-api.png 165w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/d9ecf/shopee-open-api.png 330w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/1f083/shopee-open-api.png 660w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/7a3d6/shopee-open-api.png 990w,\n/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/8802b/shopee-open-api.png 1135w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0197e1e2433780763a8f1b390c7a11e7/1f083/shopee-open-api.png\"\n            alt=\"Sampson Store\"\n            title=\"Sampson Store\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n</div>","ca